Interface DcItemData

All Known Subinterfaces:
DcItem
All Known Implementing Classes:
DcItemDataImpl, DcItemImpl
public interface DcItemData
Dublin Core metadata interface for RSS items. Provides access to DC metadata elements as defined in the Dublin Core specification.
